snippet.title: God of War: Ascension Gameplay Demo - Sony E3 2012 Press Conference
snippet.description:
There's gore galore in this gameplay demo of God of War: Ascension. Watch Kratos shed some blood at Sony's E3 2012 press conference. 

The latest news, trailers and more live from E3 2012:
http://www.ign.com/events/e3
